column5: I was planning on heading up to the cottage this upcoming weekend and I was wondering if anyone could give me a report on the ice conditions and the fishing?  I was also wondering if anyone knnew the conditions on Litlle Doe Lake!!  Thnx guys
hey i called up to my cottage sand lake [kearney] and the ice was not ready yet as of friday.these two lakes are pretty close so i would think that bernard isn't ready yet.jamie
